Air France, Delta Consider Bid for Virgin Atlantic, Times Says

-- B y   C h r i s   K a y
-- 
2011-02-20T09:06:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-20/air-france-delta-consider-bid-for-virgin-atlantic-times-says.html
  Air France-KLM  and  Delta Air Lines
Inc . are considering a joint bid for Virgin Atlantic Airways
Ltd., the airline controlled by billionaire  Richard Branson , the
 Sunday Times  reported, without saying where it got the
information.  Air France and Delta Air Lines have appointed  Goldman Sachs
Group Inc . as their adviser, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chris Kay in London at 
 ckay5@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dick Schumacher at 
 dschumacher@bloomberg.net  